{"tid":2217676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國共產黨干犯「顛覆國家政權」等行為！","createTime":"2020-09-25T15:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T16:11:43.000Z","uid":147376,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d59850e71139953d3d2936e4633a07d65ecfdddb","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076689&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzlDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=5d2c02aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076689&h=16e2fb4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076689</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">分裂國家<br />\n</span></strong>自1949年至今，中國共產黨成功武裝奪權，非法將其祖國「中華民國」一分為二：<br />\n<br />\n主要管轄臺澎金馬的中華民國（台灣）<br />\n<br />\n主要管轄大陸的中華人民共和國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">顛覆國家政權</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n軍事推翻、破壞身兼聯合國創始國及五大常任理事國之一的「中華民國」國家政權。<br />\n<br />\n在大陸一方僭建「中華人民共和國」以取代原有的「中華民國」國家體制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">恐怖活動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1927年8月「南昌暴動」<br />\n<br />\n1927年9月「秋收暴動」<br />\n<br />\n1928年1月「湘南暴動」<br />\n<br />\n中共發動多次反政府動亂，美其名為國共內戰、起義、戰役、會戰、解放戰爭，但實質是涉及組織、策劃、實施危害社會的恐怖活動，致令無辜軍民死傷無數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中共建黨之初獲蘇聯的財政津貼<br />\n<br />\n國共內戰時期獲蘇聯大批軍火支援<br />\n<br />\n從1931至1937年，「中華蘇維埃共和國」是中國共產黨在蘇聯和共產國際的支持下，於大陸建立的社會主義國家，該政權主張在全中國推翻中華民國和國民黨的統治。"},{"pid":"20641c653c1d40721ec5c5b45c5e2209b773bbd6","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68af637eddfbb2ca2422248df6c42495f317aeec","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d08b7a9fc6a97446ccd23bbac6bae84f9cef5d50","tid":2217676,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"根本勾結外國勢力。分裂中國就係佢自己"},{"pid":"2781d6340ca55b4edd70ba3629671b16c71e62c0","tid":2217676,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59417090ca4292fdc4202acab1c35321ca93c775","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf7bc2aa2ef47789fb2784e1f0433ad5236d06b9","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"中共顛覆中國政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7731db80ac0710930514383fcaa8a1c9ba649b","tid":2217676,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"847b47fef7a85e52c7b792e2a0c42550b0c407c6","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5874f1a72b8e3ea5d606cfae8288e13a38631e5c","tid":2217676,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a7b6aa89e525511059c38488da1d0e5d914283e","tid":2217676,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"唔知要等幾耐國際社會先唔承認呢個非法政權"},{"pid":"b0c6cb862c3b156a7311dad61119d98592ebce17","tid":2217676,"uid":237562,"like":0,"d